        <record id="api_endpoint_credit_check_initiate" model="thedevkitchen.api.endpoint">
            <field name="name">Initiate Credit Check</field>
            <field name="path">/api/v1/proposals/{proposal_id}/credit-checks</field>
            <field name="method">POST</field>
            <field name="module_name">thedevkitchen_estate_credit_check</field>
            <field name="protected" eval="True"/>
            <field name="tags">Proposal Credit Checks</field>
            <field name="summary">Initiate a credit check for a rental proposal</field>
            <field name="description">Initiates a credit analysis (AnĂˇlise de Ficha) for a lease proposal.
Transitions proposal state from sent/negotiation â†’ credit_check_pending.
Creates a new CreditCheck record with result=pending.

**Authorization**: Owner, Manager, or Agent (own proposals only).
**Auth Headers**: `Authorization: Bearer {jwt_token}` | `X-Openerp-Session-Id` | `X-Company-Id`

**Required Fields:**
- `insurer_name` (string, max 255 chars)

**Invariant**: Only one pending check per proposal (partial unique index, ADR-027).

**Errors:**
- 400: missing insurer_name or proposal not in sent/negotiation
- 403: agent does not own proposal
- 404: proposal not found
- 409: pending check already exists
- 422: sale proposal (credit check only for lease)</field>
            <field name="request_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "InitiateCreditCheckRequest",
  "required": ["insurer_name"],
  "properties": {
    "insurer_name": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 255, "example": "Tokio Marine"}
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="response_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "InitiateCreditCheckResponse",
  "properties": {
    "status": {"type": "string", "example": "success"},
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id":            {"type": "integer", "example": 42},
        "proposal_id":   {"type": "integer", "example": 15},
        "insurer_name":  {"type": "string",  "example": "Tokio Marine"},
        "result":        {"type": "string",  "example": "pending"},
        "requested_at":  {"type": "string",  "format": "date-time", "example": "2026-04-29T14:30:00Z"},
        "_links": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "self":     {"type": "object", "properties": {"href": {"type": "string", "example": "/api/v1/proposals/15/credit-checks/42"}}},
            "proposal": {"type": "object", "properties": {"href": {"type": "string", "example": "/api/v1/proposals/15"}}}
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="active" eval="True"/>
        </record>

        <record id="api_endpoint_credit_check_register" model="thedevkitchen.api.endpoint">
            <field name="name">Register Credit Check Result</field>
            <field name="path">/api/v1/proposals/{proposal_id}/credit-checks/{check_id}</field>
            <field name="method">PATCH</field>
            <field name="module_name">thedevkitchen_estate_credit_check</field>
            <field name="protected" eval="True"/>
            <field name="tags">Proposal Credit Checks</field>
            <field name="summary">Register the result of a pending credit check</field>
            <field name="description">Registers approved / rejected / cancelled on a pending CreditCheck.

- **approved**: Proposal â†’ accepted. Competing proposals cancelled.
- **rejected**: Proposal â†’ rejected (terminal). Queue promotion triggered.
- **cancelled**: Check cancelled. Proposal reverts to sent (FR-007c).

**Authorization**: Owner, Manager, or Agent (own proposals only).

**Required Fields:**
- `result` (`approved` | `rejected` | `cancelled`)

**Conditional Fields:**
- `rejection_reason` (required when result=`rejected`)
- `check_date` (optional, must not be future)

**Errors:**
- 400: missing result or rejection_reason
- 404: check or proposal not found
- 409: check already resolved (immutable)</field>
            <field name="request_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "RegisterCreditCheckRequest",
  "required": ["result"],
  "properties": {
    "result":           {"type": "string", "enum": ["approved", "rejected", "cancelled"], "example": "rejected"},
    "rejection_reason": {"type": "string", "example": "Renda insuficiente para o valor solicitado."},
    "check_date":       {"type": "string", "format": "date", "example": "2026-04-29"}
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="response_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "RegisterCreditCheckResponse",
  "properties": {
    "status": {"type": "string", "example": "success"},
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id":               {"type": "integer", "example": 42},
        "proposal_id":      {"type": "integer", "example": 15},
        "result":           {"type": "string",  "example": "rejected"},
        "rejection_reason": {"type": "string",  "example": "Renda insuficiente para o valor solicitado."},
        "check_date":       {"type": "string",  "format": "date", "example": "2026-04-29"}
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="active" eval="True"/>
        </record>

        <record id="api_endpoint_credit_check_list" model="thedevkitchen.api.endpoint">
            <field name="name">List Credit Checks for Proposal</field>
            <field name="path">/api/v1/proposals/{proposal_id}/credit-checks</field>
            <field name="method">GET</field>
            <field name="module_name">thedevkitchen_estate_credit_check</field>
            <field name="protected" eval="True"/>
            <field name="tags">Proposal Credit Checks</field>
            <field name="summary">List all credit checks for a proposal</field>
            <field name="description">Returns all credit check records for a given proposal, ordered by requested_at desc.

**Authorization**: Owner, Manager, or Agent (own proposals only).

**Query Parameters:**
- `result` (optional): Filter by result â€” `pending` | `approved` | `rejected` | `cancelled`
- `limit` (integer, max 100, default 100)
- `offset` (integer, default 0)</field>
            <field name="response_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "CreditCheckListResponse",
  "properties": {
    "status": {"type": "string", "example": "success"},
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "items": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id":            {"type": "integer", "example": 42},
              "insurer_name":  {"type": "string",  "example": "Tokio Marine"},
              "result":        {"type": "string",  "example": "pending"},
              "requested_at":  {"type": "string",  "format": "date-time", "example": "2026-04-29T14:30:00Z"}
            }
          }
        },
        "limit":  {"type": "integer", "example": 100},
        "offset": {"type": "integer", "example": 0},
        "_links": {"type": "object"}
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="active" eval="True"/>
        </record>

        <record id="api_endpoint_credit_history" model="thedevkitchen.api.endpoint">
            <field name="name">Get Client Credit History</field>
            <field name="path">/api/v1/clients/{partner_id}/credit-history</field>
            <field name="method">GET</field>
            <field name="module_name">thedevkitchen_estate_credit_check</field>
            <field name="protected" eval="True"/>
            <field name="tags">Client History</field>
            <field name="summary">Get full credit check history for a client</field>
            <field name="description">Returns the complete credit check history for a client (res.partner) across all proposals in the company.

**Authorization**:
- Owner/Manager: any client in their company
- Agent: only clients from their own proposals (any state). Returns 404 for out-of-scope clients (ADR-008 anti-enumeration).
- Receptionist: read-only access

**Performance**: &lt; 300ms for up to 1,000 checks per company (SC-004).

**Query Parameters:**
- `limit` (integer, max 100, default 100)
- `offset` (integer, default 0)</field>
            <field name="response_schema"><![CDATA[
{
  "type": "object",
  "title": "CreditHistoryResponse",
  "properties": {
    "status": {"type": "string", "example": "success"},
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "partner_id": {"type": "integer", "example": 7},
        "summary": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "total":     {"type": "integer", "example": 3},
            "approved":  {"type": "integer", "example": 1},
            "rejected":  {"type": "integer", "example": 2},
            "pending":   {"type": "integer", "example": 0},
            "cancelled": {"type": "integer", "example": 0}
          }
        },
        "items": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id":           {"type": "integer", "example": 42},
              "proposal_id":  {"type": "integer", "example": 15},
              "insurer_name": {"type": "string",  "example": "Tokio Marine"},
              "result":       {"type": "string",  "example": "approved"},
              "requested_at": {"type": "string",  "format": "date-time", "example": "2026-04-29T14:30:00Z"}
            }
          }
        },
        "limit":  {"type": "integer", "example": 100},
        "offset": {"type": "integer", "example": 0}
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></field>
            <field name="active" eval="True"/>
        </record>

    </data>
</odoo>
